NAME
	wizopt - set wizard options

ACCESS LEVEL
	apprentice or higher

SYNOPSIS
	wizopt
	wizopt [option]
	wizopt <option> [value]

DESCRIPTION
	This command sets various wizard changable options that are
	saved when you type 'save'.

OPTIONS:
	<none>            - Display the current settings
	<option>          - Display this option setting
	<option> <value>  - Set the option to the given value

ARGUMENTS
	autopwd <on/off>     - Automatic display of the current working 
                               directory when you change it.

SEE ALSO
	cd, options
